{"TopicId":190039,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Is it possible to change the color of lights of stock modules","CreatedByName":"Okhin","CreatedById":201182,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-27T09:32:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Okhin","CreatedById":201182,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-27T09:32:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuick question: is it possible to change the color of lights of stock modules (or, well, any other modules), I\u0027d like to create a day / night cycle on my stations and bases with redshifting light at night (instead of just shutting them of, I think it\u0027s a bad idea to have those stations without any lights), I do have Surface Mounted Lights.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-27T15:46:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/201182-okhin/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022201182\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/201182-okhin/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Okhin\u003C/a\u003E, I\u0027ve split your question off into its own thread in what I believe is the right area.\u00A0 You are looking for a mod, correct?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe thread you posted your question in is for small questions relating to real-life science and spaceflight.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-27T16:41:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmod: crew lights (might be close to what you want)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Okhin","CreatedById":201182,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-27T18:33:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223710415\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022190039\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221574869609\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/201182-okhin/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022201182\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/201182-okhin/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Okhin\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022width:0px;height:0px;margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022width:0px;height:0px;margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n, I\u0027ve split your question off into its own thread in what I believe is the right area.\u00A0 You are looking for a mod, correct?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe thread you posted your question in is for small questions relating to real-life science and spaceflight.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022width:0px;height:0px;margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022width:0px;height:0px;margin-top:0px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, crap ... thanks for moving that in the correct place (I just lost sight of what\u0027s related to KSP and real life space program it seems....)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/190933-zer0kerbal/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022190933\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/190933-zer0kerbal/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@zer0Kerbal\u003C/a\u003E well, I\u0027m searching a mod that would allow to change the lights color (as I can change the other lights). Doing the day / night shift is easy (I think a KAL-9000 correctly setup can do it in stock), it\u0027s more the ability of changing the color that I\u0027m after.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-11-27T18:34:41Z\u0022 title=\u002211/27/2019 06:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 27, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Okhin\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EFixing the layout of the post\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Manwith Noname","CreatedById":117203,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-27T19:04:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not automated but you might want to look at BULB which allows altering lights during flight.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022110959\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4501042708\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/149686-13-alshains-modlets-electric-lights-localizer-helper-advanced-tweakables-button-bulb/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s a newer recompile toward the end of the thread. Don\u0027t know if it works in 1.8.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Okhin","CreatedById":201182,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-28T10:29:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe automation part is not a problem, if those sliders can be allocated to a KAL-9000, and thanks, that\u0027s what I\u0027m looking for \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}